snippet.title: Green Ninja trailer
snippet.description:
Its the year of the frog, the celebrations are in full swing and you are on the menu!
You escape the clutches of the evil ninjas. Now you must take revenge using your unstoppable kick.

iTunes : https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/green-ninja-year-of-the-frog/id994210330?mt=8
Google Play : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nitrome.greenninja&hl=en_GB
